title: VirtualBox 7.0.12 Adds Initial Support for Linux 6.6 and openSUSE 15.5 Kernels
description:
VirtualBox 7.0.12 open-source virtualization software is now available for download with initial support for Linux kernel 6.6 and 6.5, initial support for openSUSE Leap 15.5's kernel, as well as other changes.
